# WeatherApp

WeatherApp is a simple Python program to receive and display weather information of different cities using OpenWeatherMap API.

## Features
- Display the current temperature of the city
- Displays humidity and weather conditions
- Convert temperature to Celsius (if needed)
- Display the exact time and date

## Installing
First, make sure Python 3 and pip are installed.

### How to use
Clone this repository or download the files:

   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/mrnikx/SimpleWeatherApp.git
   cd WeatherApp
